                    "body": "I don't think we have ever guaranteed anything concerning these JSON formats (which we don't control, since both are produced by third-party tools).\r\n\r\nIf you want to exchange Arrow data or metadata between Java and C++, the idiomatic and efficient solution is to use the Arrow IPC format (as a stream or file). Why are you trying to use JSON for this?",
